    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_03-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、ここって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san‚ isn’t this…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dormitory-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 5.9200225830078095
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "見ての通り\n星見市で活動していた時に使っていた寮だ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "As you can see‚\nit’s the dorm where you girls stayed when we were based in Hoshimi City.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.18668924967448,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dormitory-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 11.986689249674479
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_03-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "……まさか\n合宿って、ここでするんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hold on…\nIs this where we’re having our “bootcamp”?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.98668924967448,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dormitory-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 15.35335591634118
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "ここならみんなも初心を思い出して\nリラックスして曲作りが出来るだろ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Being here will help you remember your early days‚\nallowing you to relax and compose freely.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.75335591634115,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dormitory-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 20.186689249674526
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_03-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "そんなこと言って……合宿が急に決まったから\n他に場所を用意出来なかっただけじゃないの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Or… this bootcamp was a last-minute decision‚\nso you couldn’t find another location for the camp.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.820022583007827,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_03-szk001.m4a",
      "text": "……ここなら、泊まってもお金がかからない\n……経費節減",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Staying here won’t cost any money.\n…Cutting expenses.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.15335591634118,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dormitory-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 33.85335591634116
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "さ、さあみんな、中に入るぞ！\n早く荷物を運び込むんだ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "C-come on‚ girls! ….Inside!\nLet’s get your luggage in!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.02002258300786,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_03-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "図星ね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Bingo…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.18668924967453,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3533.333333333331,
          "startTime": 42.72002258300786
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3233.3333333333485,
          "startTime": 42.42002258300788
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2800.0000000000327,
          "startTime": 41.98668924967456
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dormitory-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 39.186689249674565
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_living-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 41.72002258300786
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_sun-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 41.98668924967453
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_03-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "うーん、懐かしいわね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ohh‚ this really takes me back!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.98668924967453,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_03-szk002.m4a",
      "text": "数ヶ月しか経ってないのに\nすごく久しぶりな気がする……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We’ve only been away a few months‚\nbut it feels like ages ago….",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.328866163889614,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_03-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "今日からまたここに泊まるんですね\n昔に戻ったみたいでちょっとワクワクします",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We get to stay here again for a while!\nI’m a little excited. It feels like we’ve gone back in time.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.99553283055628,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_03-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "夜になるとみんなでこの部屋に集まって\nよくお喋りをしたわよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "At night‚ we’d all gather in this room\nand talk a lot‚ didn’t we?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.6577651659648,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_03-szk003.m4a",
      "text": "夜の女子会……\nいろんなことを話してた……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Late night girl-talk…\nTalked about a lot of stuff…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.69109849929812,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_03-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "うん。思い付いたことがあれば、なんでも言い合って\nどんなくだらないことでも全員で話し合って……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah. If anything came to mind‚ we’d talk it over.\nNo matter how silly it was‚ we’d all discuss it together.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.02443183263144,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_03-hrk003.m4a",
      "text": "そうだったわね。せっかくだから\n合宿中は沢山女子会しようね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "True. Since we’re back here‚\nlet’s have lots of girl-talk during the camp.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.45776516596477,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_03-rei004.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっと、目的変わってますよ\n新曲作りに取り掛からないと……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey. You’ve lost sight of our objective.\nWe have to work on writing our new song.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.55776516596475,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_03-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "はい！　提案があります！\n曲作りの前にやりたいことがあります！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey! Suggestion!\nThere’s something I want to do before we get to work on the song!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.6244318326314,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_03-rei005.m4a",
      "text": "な、何よ、いきなり……\nどうしたの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wh-where did that come from?\nWhat’s up?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.25776516596464,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_03-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "この合宿でまず最初にやりたいこと……それは！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The first thing I want to do for this bootcamp is…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.59109849929796,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_comical-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 107.691098499298
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_03-rei006.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ……\nどうして寮の掃除なんてしなきゃいけないのよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "*sigh*\nTo clean the dorm?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.92443183263131,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_03-szk004.m4a",
      "text": "合宿といえば……海……水着が\nお約束……なのに……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Bootcamps usually consist of… beaches… swimsuits…\nWhy are we cleaning?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.25776516596466,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_03-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "これから数日間、この寮のお世話になるんだから\nまずはピカピカに磨いてあげないとね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ we’re going to be living here for the next few days‚\nso we need to make it sparkle first!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 123.55776516596468,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_03-skr005.m4a",
      "text": "さあさあみんな！\n気合を入れてお掃除するよー！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Come on‚ girls!\nLet’s roll up those sleeves and get cleaning!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.72443183263132,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_03-hrk004.m4a",
      "text": "さくらちゃん、張り切ってるわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sakura‚ you’re fired up‚ aren’t you?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.62443183263133,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_03-skr006.m4a",
      "text": "張り切ってるのは私だけじゃないよ\nほら、あそこを見て",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m not the only one who’s fired up.\nJust look over there.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 135.71488545735667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Satomi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_03-stm001.m4a",
      "text": "ここでサニピと月ストが暮らしていたんですね……\nこんな聖地に泊まれるなんて、感激です……",
      "translations": {
